cab.content: DOCUMENT IS THE PROPERTY OF HER BRITANNIC MAJESTY'S government cp(76) 288 June 1976COPY NO81CABINETENLARGEMENT OF THE EECNote by the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth affairs. My predecessor circulated a paper on enlargement of the european economic Community (C(76) 37) on 19 March for discussion by Cabinet on26 March. In the event, however, the paper was not taken.2. The passage of time since March has meant that a few changes need to be made and these are underlined in the new version (CP(76) 29) which I now circulate for Cabinet on 11 June.A foreign and Commonwealth Office8 June 1976
